[0.003, "o", "\u001b[1;16Het/ignore-use\u001b[2;7He_use\u001b[4;4Hetermines the size of the realpath cache to be used by PHP. This value\u001b[5;4He increased on systems where PHP opens many files to reflect the\u001b[6;5He file operations performe\u001b[7;6He: if open_basedir is set, the cache is disable\u001b[8;16Het/realpath-cache-size\u001b[9;3Healpath_cache_size\u001b[11;18He, in seconds for which to cache realpath information for a give\u001b[12;6He or directory. For systems with rarely changing files, consider incre\u001b[13;7He\u001b[14;16Het/realpath-cache\u001b[15;3Healpath_cache\u001b[17;8Hes or disables the circular reference colle\u001b[18;16Het/zend.enable\u001b[19;2Hend.enable\u001b[21;6Henabled, scripts may be written in encodings that are incompatible\u001b[22;5He scanner.  CP936, Big5, CP949 and Shift_JIS are the \u001b[30m\u001b[103mex\u001b[m\u000fample\u001b[23;3Hencodings.  To use this feature, mbstring \u001b[30m\u001b[103mex\u001b[m\u000ftension must be enable\u001b[24;3Hend.multibyte\u001b[26;14Het the default encoding for the scripts.  This value will be use\u001b[27;6Hess \"declare(encoding=...)\" directive appears at the top of the\u001b[28;11Hects if zend.multibyte is se\u001b[29;3Hend.script_e\u001b[31;19He or \u001b[30m\u001b[103mex\u001b[m\u000fclude arguments from stack traces generated for \u001b[30m\u001b[103mex\u001b[m\u000fce\u001b[32;25Hecommended to turn this setting on to prohibit the\u001b[33;7Hensitive information in stack trace\u001b[34;4Hefault Value\u001b[35;4Hevelopment Value\u001b[36;18He\u001b[37;2Hend.\u001b[30m\u001b[103mex\u001b[m\u000fception_ignore\u001b[39;11Hetting the maximum string length in an argument of a stringified stack trace\u001b[40;12He betwee\u001b[41;15Heffect when zend.\u001b[30m\u001b[103mex\u001b[m\u000fception_ignore_args is enable\u001b[42;4Hefault Value\u001b[43;4Hevelopment Value\u001b[44;18He\u001b[45;25Hecommended to set this to 0 to reduce the\u001b[46;7Hensitive information in stack trace\u001b[47;155H\u001b[0;10;7m\u000f8,2\u001b[48;4H\u001b[?25h"]
