[0.222, "o", "2026-06-08 21:02:13 0 [Warning] mariadbd: io_uring_queue_init() failed with EPERM: sysctl kernel.io_uring_disabled has the value 2, or 1 and the user of the process is not a member of sysctl kernel.io_uring_group. (see man 2 io_uring_setup).\r\n"]
